WEBVTT

00:50.049 --> 00:52.469
ALL FIGURES, INCIDENTS, LOCATIONS,
ORGANIZATIONS, AND OTHERS ARE FICTITIOUS

00:52.552 --> 00:54.971
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS WERE FILMED
SAFELY IN ACCORDANCE WITH GUIDELINES

01:04.064 --> 01:06.316
Come here, puppy!

01:23.083 --> 01:26.085
Mr. Kang passed on.

01:27.253 --> 01:28.338
Are you okay?

01:29.464 --> 01:31.382
I bet he grew on you a lot.

01:32.091 --> 01:36.471
He was deeply in love with Ms. Chae.

01:37.931 --> 01:40.016
But Ms. Chae

01:40.099 --> 01:42.227
wasn't aware of it her whole life.

01:43.478 --> 01:45.021
That really breaks my heart.

01:46.481 --> 01:47.690
I told you.

01:48.358 --> 01:51.027
If you save saying, "Thank you,"
"I'm sorry," or "I love you,"

01:51.569 --> 01:53.238
you'll regret it later.

01:54.197 --> 01:58.743
If you don't want to regret it later,
express your feelings while you can.

02:05.416 --> 02:06.417
What's wrong?

02:09.838 --> 02:12.465
I won't regret it…

02:13.800 --> 02:17.137
Yes, I know.
You're not one to regret things later.

02:17.220 --> 02:18.596
…because I'm going to tell you now.

02:20.932 --> 02:21.975
What?

02:24.811 --> 02:25.812
I want to tell you

02:26.855 --> 02:28.022
how I feel

02:29.274 --> 02:30.567
right now.

02:58.511 --> 03:00.138
Puppy!

03:01.264 --> 03:02.599
Puppy?

03:04.601 --> 03:05.852
No way.

03:07.645 --> 03:08.897
Play with me.

03:11.232 --> 03:12.442
What's your name?

03:14.777 --> 03:16.821
Why couldn't he finish what he was saying?

03:17.447 --> 03:18.531
I'm so curious.

03:19.741 --> 03:20.742
Fine, go.

03:24.203 --> 03:27.957
SHIN I-RANG LAW OFFICE

03:28.041 --> 03:30.752
Lightning Man, power!

03:32.128 --> 03:35.465
Knock it off already, kid.

03:36.007 --> 03:39.010
Come on and sit down, so we can talk.

03:40.845 --> 03:42.305
Seriously.

03:42.388 --> 03:43.389
Come here.

03:58.905 --> 04:01.157
Lightning Man, please help!

04:01.241 --> 04:03.493
Please!

04:03.576 --> 04:04.994
What's the matter, mister?

04:05.078 --> 04:09.374
I'm dying
because I have so many questions.

04:10.583 --> 04:11.876
What is it?

04:11.960 --> 04:15.546
Tell me.
Lightning Man is here to help you.

04:17.465 --> 04:19.259
Back at Haneul Park…

04:21.010 --> 04:22.679
Haneul Park?

04:22.762 --> 04:24.847
Where we first met, you know.

04:24.931 --> 04:26.432
You followed a puppy there.

04:26.516 --> 04:28.226
Oh, puppy!

04:28.309 --> 04:29.978
Right, puppy.

04:30.061 --> 04:33.439
Do you remember becoming me then?

04:33.523 --> 04:36.776
You ran with my legs
and spoke through my mouth.

04:37.402 --> 04:39.445
Yes, it was so fun!

04:40.405 --> 04:41.406
Right.

04:41.489 --> 04:45.326
But I don't remember what happened at all.

04:45.410 --> 04:48.204
So I'd like you to tell me.

04:48.830 --> 04:52.625
Did you say anything to that woman?

04:54.210 --> 04:55.920
-Woman?
-Yes.

04:56.004 --> 04:58.715
I'm talking about the woman
who was with me.

04:59.299 --> 05:00.800
A woman…

05:01.926 --> 05:03.011
Puppy.

05:04.137 --> 05:05.305
You're adorable.

05:06.014 --> 05:07.265
Hey, mister!

05:07.348 --> 05:09.892
You shouldn't touch my dog
all of a sudden like that.

05:09.976 --> 05:12.103
Don't you see he's scared?

05:13.021 --> 05:14.147
You must be startled.

05:15.398 --> 05:17.025
That woman?

05:17.525 --> 05:19.193
She scared me to death.

05:19.777 --> 05:21.988
She got angry at me and glared at me.

05:23.781 --> 05:26.784
What? She got angry and glared at you?

05:31.414 --> 05:32.415
This is bad.

05:34.876 --> 05:35.960
Really bad.

05:36.669 --> 05:38.004
I'm screwed.

05:38.087 --> 05:39.088
Is it good?

05:40.673 --> 05:42.884
Enjoy and eat up.

05:42.967 --> 05:44.135
Good morning.

05:44.218 --> 05:46.095
-Hi, Uncle.
-Good morning.

05:50.266 --> 05:51.267
I'm off to work.

05:51.893 --> 05:52.977
What about breakfast?

05:54.062 --> 05:55.521
I have no appetite.

05:55.605 --> 05:56.606
I-rang.

05:57.231 --> 05:59.233
Here. Drink this before you go.

05:59.317 --> 06:00.860
No, I'm really okay.

06:01.652 --> 06:04.197
Then take it with you for later.

06:04.280 --> 06:05.281
All right.

06:06.199 --> 06:07.909
-See you.
-Bye.

06:14.123 --> 06:15.875
Did something happen to I-rang?

06:17.502 --> 06:20.296
He's with a little boy this time.

06:20.379 --> 06:22.590
-What boy?
-What?

06:23.341 --> 06:24.425
Well…

06:25.009 --> 06:27.470
My friend's son.

06:27.553 --> 06:28.888
He's none of your concern.

06:29.847 --> 06:31.140
I was just asking.

06:31.224 --> 06:33.017
U-jin is my only concern anyway.

06:34.519 --> 06:36.104
Who's U-jin?

06:36.187 --> 06:38.856
He's none of your concern.

06:40.233 --> 06:42.819
What? Mother, do you know who he is?

06:42.902 --> 06:44.445
Yes, of course.

06:44.529 --> 06:47.031
He's a handsome little chestnut.

06:47.865 --> 06:49.075
Honey, you know him too?

06:49.158 --> 06:50.451
Of course.

06:50.535 --> 06:53.329
He's polite and adorable.

06:54.038 --> 06:56.707
What on earth? Everyone knows
about my daughter's boyfriend, but me?

06:56.791 --> 06:58.167
Yum.

07:09.470 --> 07:10.596
What's wrong?

07:11.472 --> 07:14.058
I won't regret it…

07:15.435 --> 07:18.688
Yes, I know.
You're not one to regret things later.

07:18.771 --> 07:20.189
…because I'm going to tell you now.

07:22.650 --> 07:23.776
What?

07:23.860 --> 07:24.944
I want to tell you

07:26.362 --> 07:27.572
how I feel

07:28.865 --> 07:29.866
right now.

07:31.117 --> 07:32.827
It can't be.

07:34.495 --> 07:37.248
Otherwise, it'll get really awkward.

07:54.974 --> 07:56.559
I'm off to I-rang's office.

07:56.642 --> 07:58.603
Wait, Mom.

07:58.686 --> 08:00.229
Bring this to him too.

08:00.313 --> 08:02.899
-Okay.
-Mother, let me help you. It looks heavy.

08:02.982 --> 08:05.526
-Will you?
-I'll go with her, honey.

08:05.610 --> 08:07.820
Grandma, me too!

08:08.446 --> 08:10.907
-I want to help out too.
-What?

08:12.033 --> 08:13.784
-Isn't it heavy?
-No.

08:13.868 --> 08:16.245
Me too! I want to go too!

08:16.829 --> 08:19.957
Don't you want to know
who your parents are?

08:20.875 --> 08:22.460
I'm not sure.

08:23.419 --> 08:25.004
I don't remember.

08:26.714 --> 08:27.924
I see.

08:30.301 --> 08:33.513
What's that in your pocket?

08:35.640 --> 08:37.058
What's this?

08:38.309 --> 08:39.477
A golf ball?

08:40.436 --> 08:42.647
Can you hand it to me?

08:43.231 --> 08:44.315
Here you go.

08:47.443 --> 08:49.487
What… Where did it go?

08:54.200 --> 08:56.994
I guess you had it with you
in your last moment.

08:59.372 --> 09:01.624
Can I take a close look at it?

09:04.043 --> 09:05.169
"GSG"?

09:07.046 --> 09:09.006
Uncle!

09:09.590 --> 09:13.094
-Uncle, we're here.
-Da-bong!

09:15.513 --> 09:17.056
Wow!

09:17.139 --> 09:18.975
She's so cute!

09:43.291 --> 09:44.792
Uncle, what's wrong?

09:48.754 --> 09:50.298
You like Heartsping?

09:52.675 --> 09:54.260
Why do you even ask? You know I do.

09:59.724 --> 10:03.686
I'll give you all my love

10:03.769 --> 10:04.979
Wow!

10:05.062 --> 10:08.441
-I'll give you tons and tons of love
-I'll give you tons and tons of love

10:08.524 --> 10:12.528
-Heartsping time full of love
-Heartsping time full of love

10:12.612 --> 10:15.615
-Chu-chu, Heartsping
-Chu-chu, Heartsping

10:19.910 --> 10:23.372
-Heartsping time full of love
-Heartsping time full of love

10:23.456 --> 10:26.250
-Chu-chu, Heartsping
-Chu-chu, Heartsping

10:27.877 --> 10:29.962
-Heartsping, power!
-Heartsping, power!

10:30.046 --> 10:31.047
Let's go!

10:31.130 --> 10:32.340
I-rang, it's time to come back.

10:32.423 --> 10:33.674
No, wait.

10:34.300 --> 10:35.926
After we feed those kids.

10:36.677 --> 10:40.514
Kids, let's eat
before you have some more fun.

10:43.309 --> 10:44.769
-Looks yummy!
-It looks good!

10:46.395 --> 10:47.480
Delicious.

10:47.563 --> 10:48.689
Eat up.

10:49.940 --> 10:51.400
I want this one.

10:52.443 --> 10:53.694
It's tasty.

10:54.737 --> 10:55.905
It's yummy.

11:10.836 --> 11:12.046
How do you do?

11:18.886 --> 11:20.971
Let's go have fun.

11:22.973 --> 11:24.225
How do you morning.

11:38.489 --> 11:40.533
What's wrong, Attorney Shin?
You're scaring me.

11:42.493 --> 11:43.619
Am I scary?

11:45.788 --> 11:47.665
This lady thinks I'm scary.

11:47.748 --> 11:51.293
-Nanny-nanny-boo-boo!
-Nanny-nanny-boo-boo!

11:51.377 --> 11:55.005
-She's a scaredy-cat for an adult!
-She's a scaredy-cat for an adult!

11:57.675 --> 12:00.469
-Lightning Man, off to go!
-Let's go!

12:01.053 --> 12:02.596
Let's go!

12:04.390 --> 12:06.684
Da-bong! Oh, hello.

12:06.767 --> 12:09.353
If that's an act,
he should be an Oscar winner.

12:09.437 --> 12:11.355
It must be a rascal this time.

12:11.439 --> 12:12.815
Excuse me.

12:12.898 --> 12:16.193
Wait for me! Goodness.

12:17.069 --> 12:18.195
Yes, I know.

12:19.280 --> 12:21.115
But I just can't get used to it.

12:25.828 --> 12:27.079
Whoosh!

12:28.664 --> 12:29.665
That's dangerous!

12:29.748 --> 12:31.834
-It's fun.
-Mommy!

12:31.917 --> 12:33.836
Lightning power!

12:33.919 --> 12:36.172
Auntie, guess what?

12:36.922 --> 12:40.050
My uncle is the most affectionate man
in the whole world.

12:40.634 --> 12:41.635
Affectionate?

12:42.219 --> 12:43.929
Do you know what that means?

12:44.638 --> 12:46.348
It means to feel for someone.

12:48.142 --> 12:52.605
He cries with me when I'm sad.

12:53.564 --> 12:56.692
When I'm happy, he's excited too.

12:57.902 --> 12:59.612
That's not easy, you know.

13:02.740 --> 13:05.284
That's why he's the best.

13:20.674 --> 13:22.134
Anyway,

13:22.218 --> 13:24.553
why do you look at him like that?

13:26.347 --> 13:27.348
Me?

13:28.015 --> 13:29.099
How did I look at him?

13:30.476 --> 13:33.229
How my mom looks at my dad.

13:34.188 --> 13:37.066
Kind eyes. Warm eyes.

13:37.983 --> 13:39.109
That's not true.

13:43.864 --> 13:45.491
Slow down. Slow…

13:46.325 --> 13:47.701
-Wait, no.
-Lightning power!

13:47.785 --> 13:49.203
You can't come up here.

13:54.667 --> 13:56.210
-I-rang, are you okay?
-Uncle!

13:56.293 --> 13:58.420
-What…
-Attorney Shin, are you okay?

13:58.504 --> 14:00.464
-What am I doing here?
-Gosh.

14:00.548 --> 14:01.799
Come out of there.

14:01.882 --> 14:04.176
Careful.

14:09.890 --> 14:11.433
Attorney Han…

14:13.185 --> 14:15.396
How long are you going to play here?

14:16.730 --> 14:18.482
What I'm trying to say is…

14:20.442 --> 14:22.820
Aren't you going to work?
We have work to do.

14:25.656 --> 14:26.699
Oh, gosh.

14:26.782 --> 14:28.826
I-rang, are you okay?

14:28.909 --> 14:29.952
Uncle.

14:30.035 --> 14:32.705
Da-bong, why is she so angry?

14:34.123 --> 14:36.375
She wasn't when she was with me.

14:37.501 --> 14:39.712
Maybe it's because you teased her earlier.

14:41.171 --> 14:44.049
What? I teased her?

14:44.133 --> 14:46.719
-Well…
-Earlier. Don't you remember?

14:46.802 --> 14:48.804
We said, "Nanny-nanny-boo-boo,"

14:48.888 --> 14:51.098
-and wiggled our butts at her.
-What?

14:51.682 --> 14:55.269
"Nanny-nanny-boo-boo!" Like this.

14:55.352 --> 14:56.770
I did that?

14:56.854 --> 14:58.647
Stop it.

14:58.731 --> 15:00.858
You did this too.

15:17.333 --> 15:19.835
How exactly did I look at Attorney Shin?

15:28.719 --> 15:29.970
I'm back.

15:32.473 --> 15:33.766
That was quick.

15:35.476 --> 15:36.477
Right.

15:40.606 --> 15:41.607
Are you perhaps

15:42.650 --> 15:43.692
angry at me?

15:43.776 --> 15:45.152
Why would I be angry?

15:45.235 --> 15:47.488
Because earlier…

15:50.532 --> 15:51.617
I teased you.

15:51.700 --> 15:53.744
No, I knew you were possessed.

15:56.413 --> 15:59.083
Is it okay
to get possessed this often, though?

16:00.834 --> 16:02.086
What?

16:02.169 --> 16:03.879
You know in movies,

16:03.963 --> 16:08.175
it's physically damaging
to interact with spiritual beings.

16:10.511 --> 16:12.388
It's not the case for me.

16:12.471 --> 16:14.640
The ghosts I encounter

16:15.432 --> 16:17.893
are pretty much like humans.

16:25.150 --> 16:27.111
Did you discover anything about the boy?

16:28.237 --> 16:30.155
He had a golf ball with him.

16:31.949 --> 16:33.075
A golf ball?

16:33.158 --> 16:38.122
Yes, the ball had "GSG" printed on it.

16:38.706 --> 16:40.374
But I'm not sure what it means.

16:40.457 --> 16:44.920
Golf driving ranges have
their initials printed on golf balls.

16:45.421 --> 16:46.839
This could be one.

16:48.716 --> 16:50.175
It sounds plausible.

16:51.510 --> 16:55.806
If the boy obtained the golf ball
right before he died,

16:55.889 --> 16:59.143
it may be an important clue
about where he died.

16:59.226 --> 17:01.478
SEOUL, GSG, SEOCHO-DONG,
GOLF DRIVING RANGE

17:07.151 --> 17:11.030
I didn't know there were
this many golf ranges in Seoul.

17:12.698 --> 17:14.450
This won't do.

17:22.374 --> 17:24.418
Do you have another idea?

17:25.794 --> 17:26.920
No.

17:30.090 --> 17:32.593
Do you have something to tell me?

17:34.303 --> 17:35.596
I don't.

17:36.930 --> 17:39.600
Anyone can tell you have something to say.

17:42.770 --> 17:46.273
What were you going to tell me
at Haneul Park yesterday?

17:47.566 --> 17:48.776
What?

17:48.859 --> 17:50.235
That woman?

17:50.819 --> 17:52.279
She scared me to death.

17:52.946 --> 17:55.949
She got angry at me and glared at me.

17:58.827 --> 17:59.828
That…

18:01.246 --> 18:02.289
was nothing.

18:03.665 --> 18:04.666
Really,

18:05.667 --> 18:06.919
it was nothing.

18:08.378 --> 18:09.379
Don't mind it.

18:11.298 --> 18:13.926
Where was that golf ball again?

18:14.885 --> 18:16.804
Here… Wait, no.

18:19.223 --> 18:20.307
Is it here?

18:20.891 --> 18:21.934
Where is that ball?

18:23.143 --> 18:24.269
What the heck.

18:25.771 --> 18:27.481
It really was nothing.

18:31.068 --> 18:34.571
SHIN I-RANG, HAN NA-HYUN

18:59.054 --> 19:00.055
Hi, Dad.

19:00.139 --> 19:02.307
Hi, Na-hyun. Did you leave work?

19:02.391 --> 19:04.309
Not yet. What's up?

19:04.393 --> 19:06.520
I'm calling about

19:07.146 --> 19:08.480
your boss from Taebaek.

19:09.231 --> 19:11.525
-Yang Do-kyung?
-Yes, him.

19:11.608 --> 19:14.528
He called me a while ago.

19:16.196 --> 19:17.781
Hello, sir.

19:17.865 --> 19:20.117
This is Managing Partner Yang Do-kyung
of Taebaek.

19:20.200 --> 19:22.452
We met in front of Attorney Han's office
the other day.

19:23.996 --> 19:26.206
Yes, of course. Hello, sir.

19:27.374 --> 19:30.919
Please don't be too polite with me.
I'm a close friend of your daughter's.

19:31.003 --> 19:33.172
You can call me Do-kyung.

19:33.255 --> 19:37.301
Oh, goodness. Even so, I can't do that.

19:38.886 --> 19:40.512
I'm calling

19:40.596 --> 19:43.765
to ask how you've been feeling
since that day.

19:44.349 --> 19:47.686
I see. I'm feeling totally fine.

19:48.270 --> 19:49.771
That's a relief.

19:50.939 --> 19:55.194
But it's easy to have body aches
and health issues over time

19:55.277 --> 19:59.281
even if you feel okay at first
after a car accident.

19:59.364 --> 20:03.368
No, I'm really okay.

20:03.452 --> 20:06.371
No. I'm not okay, sir.

20:07.539 --> 20:11.084
You're the father of Attorney Han
who used to be my colleague for years.

20:11.793 --> 20:14.171
I can't just leave everything up
to the insurance company.

20:15.005 --> 20:18.842
Near my office, there's a holistic clinic
with good acupuncture skills.

20:18.926 --> 20:21.053
Do you have time tomorrow?

20:22.804 --> 20:26.934
Before I knew it, I agreed
to an appointment tomorrow at 3:00 p.m.

20:27.517 --> 20:29.478
Why does he keep doing this?

20:29.561 --> 20:30.896
Na-hyun.

20:30.979 --> 20:34.274
Is there anything going on
between you and him?

20:34.358 --> 20:36.568
What are you talking about?
There's nothing at all.

20:37.736 --> 20:40.489
Maybe he's just kind-hearted then.

20:41.573 --> 20:42.658
Dad.

20:42.741 --> 20:45.786
Call him now and refuse his offer, okay?

20:45.869 --> 20:48.330
Sure, I'll do that.

20:48.413 --> 20:50.207
Okay, bye.

21:00.759 --> 21:01.843
Hello, sir.

21:01.927 --> 21:05.013
I really shouldn't go, after all.

21:05.097 --> 21:06.265
You're not coming?

21:06.890 --> 21:07.891
Why all of a sudden?

21:07.975 --> 21:09.309
Because…

21:09.935 --> 21:12.354
I'm not really sick,

21:12.437 --> 21:14.481
and I'm a bit busy.

21:15.274 --> 21:18.151
-And…
-Are you sure there's no other reason?

21:20.404 --> 21:23.115
The thing is, Na-hyun…

21:23.907 --> 21:25.158
Attorney Han?

21:27.452 --> 21:30.330
My daughter isn't fond of it.

21:31.415 --> 21:33.083
Oh, dear. I'm sorry, sir.

21:33.166 --> 21:35.460
I got a customer. I need to go.

21:35.544 --> 21:37.629
-Excuse me. Goodbye.
-Wait, sir.

21:37.713 --> 21:39.047
Hello?

21:39.756 --> 21:40.757
Sir?

21:45.595 --> 21:47.431
Oh, boy.

21:50.142 --> 21:53.145
PITTER-PATTER BUTCHER-STYLE BBQ

22:05.324 --> 22:06.575
Chief Prosecutor Yang?

22:06.658 --> 22:07.659
Hello.

22:07.743 --> 22:09.619
What brings you here?

22:09.703 --> 22:12.331
I'm here for dinner.

22:13.332 --> 22:15.000
Are you closed already?

22:15.083 --> 22:16.251
No.

22:16.752 --> 22:19.796
Today's a regular closing day. I'm sorry.

22:19.880 --> 22:21.798
Well, that's a bummer.

22:21.882 --> 22:23.925
I'll come again another time.

22:24.718 --> 22:25.886
Wait.

22:28.346 --> 22:31.850
I was meaning to invite you over
for a meal anyway.

22:31.933 --> 22:33.226
Why don't you come to my home?

22:33.810 --> 22:36.480
No, I can't cause you a sudden nuisance.

22:36.563 --> 22:39.691
Please don't say that.
I won't be at ease otherwise.

22:39.775 --> 22:40.776
Please come.

22:41.902 --> 22:44.279
Then, excuse me for a while.

22:51.995 --> 22:54.206
Take your time and help yourself.

22:54.289 --> 22:57.209
Let me go wrap things up
at the restaurant.

22:57.292 --> 22:59.878
-Sure, feel free to do so.
-Okay.

23:59.396 --> 24:01.940
Are you looking for something?

24:02.023 --> 24:03.525
No, not at all.

24:03.608 --> 24:06.027
I finished eating
and didn't know where you were.

24:06.111 --> 24:07.112
Dear me.

24:07.696 --> 24:10.240
I was occupied with work
leaving my guest unattended.

24:10.323 --> 24:13.118
Don't mention it.
I'm to blame for my sudden visit.

24:13.201 --> 24:15.620
I enjoyed dinner thanks to you.

24:16.538 --> 24:17.539
That's good to hear.

24:17.622 --> 24:19.082
I'll come again another time.

24:19.166 --> 24:20.458
Sure.

24:21.293 --> 24:24.296
PITTER-PATTER BUTCHER-STYLE BBQ

25:11.134 --> 25:14.054
Are you looking for something?

25:14.137 --> 25:15.639
No, not at all.

25:15.722 --> 25:17.933
I finished eating
and didn't know where you were.

25:18.975 --> 25:21.311
Why was he trying
to check the master bedroom?

25:23.855 --> 25:24.856
Did he…

25:25.857 --> 25:27.692
leave any records behind?

25:28.485 --> 25:29.694
Records?

25:30.278 --> 25:32.948
The case materials didn't include
any of his notebooks

25:33.573 --> 25:36.117
or key materials about the case.

25:51.383 --> 25:53.260
"Good Shot Golf"?

25:56.471 --> 25:58.932
GOOD SHOT GOLF DRIVING RANGE

26:07.274 --> 26:08.692
Found it.

26:08.775 --> 26:09.901
Really?

26:10.652 --> 26:13.613
Will I get to find my mom and dad soon?

26:15.532 --> 26:19.327
It's too late today,
so let's go home and sleep.

26:19.411 --> 26:22.038
We'll discuss it
with Attorney Han again tomorrow.

26:23.331 --> 26:27.168
Can I stay next to the old lady
at your place?

26:28.420 --> 26:29.462
Why?

26:30.046 --> 26:32.132
I like being with her.

26:35.051 --> 26:36.678
Go ahead.

26:37.262 --> 26:38.888
Yay!

26:40.557 --> 26:41.558
Whoosh!

26:45.103 --> 26:46.229
Wait just a little.

26:47.022 --> 26:50.317
I'll find your mom for you soon.

26:58.491 --> 27:00.243
It pisses me off the more I think of it.

27:12.297 --> 27:14.049
She's not here yet.

27:19.763 --> 27:21.890
It was nothing? What is he playing at?

27:29.939 --> 27:32.984
ATTORNEY SHIN I-RANG

27:34.402 --> 27:36.696
The number you've dialed is not available.
You'll be forwarded…

27:41.076 --> 27:43.203
Attorney Han isn't one to be late.

27:43.787 --> 27:45.497
Who's Attorney Han?

27:47.123 --> 27:50.377
She was the one
at Haneul Park and the playground.

27:50.460 --> 27:51.836
You said she got angry at me.

27:51.920 --> 27:53.797
No.

27:53.880 --> 27:56.591
The puppy owner is the one who got angry.

27:57.300 --> 28:00.845
She got really mad at me
for startling her puppy.

28:02.055 --> 28:04.933
What? It wasn't Attorney Han?

28:05.517 --> 28:09.729
She was looking at you excitedly
as if she was waiting for something.

28:10.939 --> 28:14.192
Her face was lit up like
right before opening a Christmas gift.

28:16.778 --> 28:17.779
She was…

28:19.114 --> 28:20.198
looking excited?

28:23.326 --> 28:24.619
Geez.

28:24.702 --> 28:26.287
I was worried for nothing.

28:28.373 --> 28:30.125
ATTORNEY HAN NA-HYUN

28:33.420 --> 28:35.672
Is she taking her time
because she feels awkward?

28:57.026 --> 28:59.529
SHIN I-RANG, HAN NA-HYUN
LAW OFFICE

29:12.917 --> 29:14.377
I'm here.

29:26.806 --> 29:27.807
Come in.

29:32.812 --> 29:34.397
How may I help you?

29:41.362 --> 29:44.073
Ma'am, how may I help you?

29:44.157 --> 29:45.450
My child.

29:45.533 --> 29:47.619
My child is missing.

29:47.702 --> 29:49.329
Please find my child for me.

29:49.412 --> 29:51.414
Please find him!

29:51.498 --> 29:53.208
-Find him for me!
-Calm down.

29:53.291 --> 29:55.460
-Please find my child.
-Ma'am.

29:56.044 --> 29:57.086
You're looking for a child?

29:57.170 --> 29:59.589
He's in first or second grade.

29:59.672 --> 30:02.634
I think he got into an accident
at Good Shot Golf Driving Range.

30:02.717 --> 30:03.927
Just a moment.

30:09.098 --> 30:10.558
Stay still.

30:11.851 --> 30:14.312
Good Shot Golf closed down in 2020.

30:14.896 --> 30:16.606
And no accidents were reported.

30:17.190 --> 30:20.068
Are there any records
about a child in yellow rain boots?

30:20.652 --> 30:23.404
I'd appreciate it
if you could focus on fatal accidents.

30:28.993 --> 30:30.328
CASE INFORMATION: YELLOW RAIN BOOTS
NO DATA

30:30.411 --> 30:31.788
No records of that, either.

30:32.622 --> 30:33.873
Why do you ask, though?

30:34.624 --> 30:36.251
Is it related to a crime?

30:36.876 --> 30:39.462
I'm not sure.

30:40.713 --> 30:43.007
Anyway, thank you.

30:45.301 --> 30:46.928
Lightning Man, let's go.

30:53.184 --> 30:55.144
Is he mentally ill?

30:59.691 --> 31:02.110
PITTER-PATTER BUTCHER-STYLE BBQ

31:04.153 --> 31:06.072
When are we meeting Da-bong?

31:06.155 --> 31:07.615
Later in the evening.

31:09.701 --> 31:11.619
I want to play with her now.

31:15.540 --> 31:17.750
GOOD SHOT GOLF DRIVING RANGE

31:20.461 --> 31:22.255
THERE IS NO INFORMATION FOR THIS LOCATION

31:24.966 --> 31:26.342
I should just go there myself.

31:31.681 --> 31:34.392
Why don't we have something delicious?

31:34.475 --> 31:35.476
What do you like?

31:35.560 --> 31:36.644
Hamburger? Pizza?

31:36.728 --> 31:38.354
-Pizza!
-Pizza?

31:39.272 --> 31:40.690
I like pizza too.

31:47.071 --> 31:50.325
You're the first ghost
with a similar taste in food.

31:51.743 --> 31:54.537
Lightning Man, listen carefully.

31:54.621 --> 31:56.414
Later when you smell pizza,

31:56.497 --> 31:59.792
you'll become me
like the other day at the playground.

31:59.876 --> 32:03.254
When you do, eat all you want, okay?

32:03.838 --> 32:04.881
Okay!

32:05.381 --> 32:06.758
What kind of pizza should it be?

32:08.176 --> 32:10.261
-Sweet potato?
-Sweet potato!

32:10.345 --> 32:11.971
-Bulgogi?
-Bulgogi.

32:14.557 --> 32:15.725
Let's go.

32:27.403 --> 32:28.404
I want to…

32:30.740 --> 32:32.200
divorce my wife.

32:34.035 --> 32:38.331
May I ask why you want to get a divorce?

32:38.414 --> 32:40.166
When she's with me…

32:42.460 --> 32:43.461
she suffers.

32:45.588 --> 32:47.048
This is the only way

32:48.925 --> 32:50.176
to protect my wife.

33:13.199 --> 33:15.535
Thanks for the pizza, mister.

33:15.618 --> 33:20.540
Lightning Man, splash a bit of water
on my face when you're done, okay?

33:28.798 --> 33:30.091
Wow.

33:30.174 --> 33:32.802
You finished the whole pan.

33:33.761 --> 33:35.930
It was really good.

33:36.973 --> 33:39.851
I see. What matters is that you're happy.

33:42.687 --> 33:45.982
Let me go wash my hands.
Wait a little here.

34:02.290 --> 34:04.083
Hello, sir.

34:04.167 --> 34:05.334
Hello, lieutenant.

34:05.918 --> 34:08.921
You came a bit early.
You have to wait around five minutes.

34:09.005 --> 34:10.631
That's all right. I can wait.

34:11.257 --> 34:12.258
Okay.

34:12.341 --> 34:15.970
You come here to buy pizza every day.
I bet your son's crazy about pizza.

34:16.054 --> 34:17.096
Yes.

34:17.180 --> 34:19.974
He especially loves your pizza.

34:20.058 --> 34:21.684
I'm so grateful.

34:21.768 --> 34:24.312
Bring him over sometime.
I'll give you a lot of extras.

34:25.188 --> 34:27.857
I'd love that,
but he's very shy around others.

34:27.940 --> 34:29.442
Kids at that age are all…

34:30.193 --> 34:32.070
-I'd like to pay the bill.
-Sure.

34:32.153 --> 34:35.156
-That will be 42,000 won.
-I really enjoyed it.

34:37.200 --> 34:38.326
Attorney Shin?

34:38.951 --> 34:40.328
Who…

34:40.912 --> 34:42.747
Don't you remember me?

34:42.830 --> 34:44.957
I'm Lieutenant Cho Chi-yeong
of Seocho Police Station.

34:46.459 --> 34:48.711
Mr. Shin,
your attorney is here to see you.

34:52.548 --> 34:55.968
Wow, you even have a detective friend?

34:56.677 --> 34:58.471
You're so cool!

34:58.554 --> 35:02.558
We met when you were arrested
for assaulting teenagers.

35:03.184 --> 35:05.978
Mister, you hit someone?

35:07.230 --> 35:10.274
Come on. Those teenagers
were found to be the assailants.

35:10.983 --> 35:12.276
Oh, right. They indeed were.

35:12.360 --> 35:13.694
I'm sorry. My mistake.

35:13.778 --> 35:15.154
That's okay.

35:16.322 --> 35:18.199
You might know since you're a detective.

35:19.242 --> 35:21.536
I'm looking for a child
who got into an accident

35:21.619 --> 35:23.704
at Good Shot Golf Driving Range.

35:24.288 --> 35:25.748
Do you perhaps know anything?

35:25.832 --> 35:28.042
An accident
at Good Shot Golf Driving Range?

35:28.126 --> 35:29.710
Yes…

35:30.419 --> 35:33.256
it's a boy in first or second grade.

35:33.339 --> 35:34.966
He was in yellow rain boots.

35:36.926 --> 35:38.094
I'm not sure.

35:38.678 --> 35:41.347
I don't recall of any such cases.
What is this about?

35:43.015 --> 35:45.101
He's a boy I know,

35:45.184 --> 35:47.728
and he can't remember
how he got into the accident.

35:48.437 --> 35:50.064
I wondered if you knew anything.

35:51.149 --> 35:52.567
It's fine if you don't.

35:52.650 --> 35:54.318
Your payment is all done, sir.

35:54.402 --> 35:55.736
Thank you.

35:55.820 --> 35:57.029
I'll be going.

35:57.113 --> 35:58.739
-Okay. Take care, sir.
-Bye.

36:13.045 --> 36:16.340
Hi, Corporal Lee. Were there any
missing person reports while I was away?

36:16.424 --> 36:19.051
Yes, I was meaning to tell you.

36:19.135 --> 36:21.637
But an elementary student
was reported missing a while ago.

36:21.721 --> 36:22.847
An elementary student?

36:23.431 --> 36:25.391
It's an eight-year-old boy in first grade.

36:26.184 --> 36:27.185
Description?

36:27.268 --> 36:30.188
He was wearing a white sweatshirt
and yellow rain boots.

36:32.315 --> 36:35.318
It's a boy in first or second grade.

36:35.401 --> 36:36.986
He was in yellow rain boots.

36:39.655 --> 36:41.532
Can you text me the details?

36:42.033 --> 36:43.201
Yes, sir.

36:43.284 --> 36:44.285
Okay.

36:47.914 --> 36:48.915
SHIN I-RANG LAW OFFICE

36:53.127 --> 36:54.629
PITTER-PATTER BUTCHER-STYLE BBQ

37:01.636 --> 37:03.387
Our son slept in that day.

37:05.056 --> 37:06.807
He usually woke up with no problem,

37:07.391 --> 37:09.310
but it was different that day.

37:10.686 --> 37:14.065
I checked his forehead,
and he had a slight fever.

37:14.732 --> 37:17.401
-Go on. Have a good day.
-Okay, bye.

37:17.485 --> 37:20.238
-My wife went to work earlier than me…
-Si-ho.

37:20.321 --> 37:22.156
…so I always took him to school.

37:26.369 --> 37:29.080
I couldn't skip work suddenly
just because he was sick.

37:29.622 --> 37:31.749
Si-ho, I got a good idea.

37:31.832 --> 37:32.959
Wait here.

37:33.042 --> 37:36.796
I took his yellow rain boots out
to cheer him up.

37:38.214 --> 37:39.840
It was raining that day…

37:40.633 --> 37:43.344
-Ta-da.
-…and he liked wearing rain boots.

37:44.512 --> 37:47.098
Open the door. Wait, the umbrella first.

37:50.393 --> 37:51.894
Si-ho, have fun at school.

37:51.978 --> 37:53.437
Okay? Close the door.

37:53.521 --> 37:55.273
YONGJIN DELIVERY

37:55.356 --> 37:56.607
Go on.

38:10.413 --> 38:11.747
I had no idea…

38:14.041 --> 38:16.252
that would be my last time with him.

38:20.673 --> 38:21.882
The last?

38:22.800 --> 38:24.802
Just like other working couples,

38:25.886 --> 38:28.639
we took turns picking up our son.

38:29.765 --> 38:31.142
It was my wife's turn that day.

38:31.767 --> 38:33.019
But then…

38:34.103 --> 38:37.982
YONGJIN DELIVERY

38:39.483 --> 38:42.611
Can you pick up our son today? Sorry.

38:45.823 --> 38:47.825
SCHOOL BUS DROP-OFF AND PICK-UP

38:50.786 --> 38:54.790
YONGJIN DELIVERY

38:55.499 --> 38:57.918
I rushed there
after checking her text late.

38:58.919 --> 39:00.588
But our son was already gone.

39:00.671 --> 39:01.881
Si-ho?

39:03.841 --> 39:05.051
Si-ho.

39:06.427 --> 39:07.470
Si-ho?

39:08.095 --> 39:09.096
Si-ho.

39:11.682 --> 39:12.683
Si-ho!

39:13.893 --> 39:14.894
Si-ho.

39:15.561 --> 39:16.687
Si-ho?

39:18.397 --> 39:19.523
Si-ho!

39:20.649 --> 39:21.650
Si-ho!

39:22.777 --> 39:23.986
Si-ho.

39:24.612 --> 39:25.613
Sir.

39:25.696 --> 39:27.782
Have you seen a boy this tall?

39:27.865 --> 39:29.825
He's wearing a blue backpack.

39:29.909 --> 39:31.118
He's a first grader.

39:31.202 --> 39:34.663
Oh, yellow rain boots.
He's wearing yellow rain boots.

39:34.747 --> 39:35.790
Have you seen him?

39:36.374 --> 39:37.541
I haven't.

39:37.625 --> 39:39.502
Si-ho!

39:42.213 --> 39:44.131
Yoon Si-ho!

39:46.926 --> 39:48.302
Si-ho!

39:49.387 --> 39:51.597
Where on earth are you?

39:53.891 --> 39:55.601
Our son went missing,

39:57.269 --> 39:58.521
and my wife and I…

40:03.234 --> 40:04.735
fell into despair.

40:19.583 --> 40:21.585
PITTER-PATTER BUTCHER-STYLE BBQ

40:55.327 --> 40:56.370
Lieutenant Cho?

40:58.622 --> 41:02.001
I checked, and there really was
an elementary student reported missing.

41:02.084 --> 41:04.170
I wanted to talk to you more in detail.

41:05.087 --> 41:06.255
That's good.

41:06.839 --> 41:09.758
Why don't we
look around this place together?

41:10.342 --> 41:13.179
It might be faster to look for him
together than explaining it.

41:13.846 --> 41:16.056
Do you think the boy is here?

41:18.476 --> 41:19.477
Yes.

41:19.560 --> 41:21.812
I can't explain why in detail,

41:21.896 --> 41:22.897
but I believe so.

41:24.356 --> 41:26.150
Will you come with me?

41:27.234 --> 41:28.944
If a boy is in danger, we must save him.

41:30.696 --> 41:31.864
-Thank you.
-My pleasure.

41:37.411 --> 41:39.121
Could you wait just a moment?

41:39.205 --> 41:40.206
Sure.

41:51.133 --> 41:55.763
I want you to wait here
while I'm away with the detective.

41:56.347 --> 41:58.015
Can't I go with you?

42:01.727 --> 42:05.981
Even on TV,
there are shows only for adults, right?

42:06.065 --> 42:07.316
Now is the same.

42:08.317 --> 42:11.195
It may be dangerous for a boy inside.

42:13.072 --> 42:15.115
But I want to go together.

42:15.824 --> 42:17.743
It won't be long.

42:18.911 --> 42:21.163
I'm scared of being alone.

42:30.798 --> 42:33.801
-Lightning Man!
-Wow!

42:34.468 --> 42:36.512
Watch this, okay?

42:36.595 --> 42:37.763
Okay.

42:49.066 --> 42:51.026
-Shall we?
-Okay.

42:51.694 --> 42:53.237
You're even having your gun ready?

42:54.029 --> 42:55.573
The world can be quite dangerous.

42:56.407 --> 42:58.242
I'm in good hands with you around.

42:58.993 --> 43:00.035
-Let's go.
-Okay.

43:15.342 --> 43:16.719
DRIVING RANGE

43:36.822 --> 43:37.823
Anyway,

43:38.574 --> 43:41.285
how did you get the information
about this place?

43:42.536 --> 43:43.537
Well…

43:45.789 --> 43:47.791
You can't tell me that either?

43:48.417 --> 43:51.170
I'm sorry. Even if I told you,
you wouldn't believe me.

44:04.183 --> 44:06.894
Where are Corporal Park
and Lieutenant Kim?

44:06.977 --> 44:08.687
They're off on a drunk person report.

44:10.481 --> 44:12.274
You get ready then.

44:12.358 --> 44:15.486
-We got a missing person report just now.
-A missing person?

44:15.569 --> 44:17.363
Yes, it's under wraps for now.

44:17.446 --> 44:20.240
There hasn't been any proof of kidnapping
or contact from the kidnapper.

44:20.324 --> 44:22.076
So, canvass the area for now.

44:22.576 --> 44:25.996
I emailed the flyer to you.
Check it and print copies.

44:29.124 --> 44:31.043
REQUEST FOR MISSING CHILD
FLYER DISTRIBUTION

44:34.922 --> 44:37.174
KWON YE-JUN [8-YEAR-OLD BOY]
117 CM TALL, SLIM

44:39.051 --> 44:41.637
WEARING WHITE SWEATSHIRT, JEANS,
YELLOW RAIN BOOTS

44:43.222 --> 44:46.225
Are there any records
about a child in yellow rain boots?

44:46.809 --> 44:49.436
I'd appreciate it
if you could focus on fatal accidents.

45:06.537 --> 45:08.497
Did you hear that just now?

45:10.290 --> 45:13.085
There's a construction site nearby.
I think it's coming from there.

45:13.752 --> 45:14.753
Is it?

45:17.840 --> 45:18.882
I don't think so.

45:20.342 --> 45:21.677
It's close by.

45:23.554 --> 45:26.056
The boy who was reported missing.

45:26.140 --> 45:27.391
When was he reported missing?

45:27.474 --> 45:28.559
This morning.

45:28.642 --> 45:29.977
This morning?

45:31.520 --> 45:32.938
That makes no sense.

45:41.488 --> 45:42.656
There's another.

45:43.157 --> 45:44.158
What do you mean?

45:44.241 --> 45:45.742
There's another child missing.

45:50.080 --> 45:51.290
Attorney Shin.

45:51.999 --> 45:53.041
Did you perhaps…

45:54.209 --> 45:56.962
visit this place
when it was a shaman's house?

45:59.173 --> 46:00.507
How did you know?

46:01.842 --> 46:02.885
A child ghost.

46:03.886 --> 46:05.762
-What?
-Excuse me,

46:05.846 --> 46:08.557
but could you tell me
your son's name and birth date?

46:10.058 --> 46:11.435
What for…

46:12.895 --> 46:14.771
Power!

46:17.983 --> 46:19.568
I found out who the boy is.

46:20.486 --> 46:22.946
Born on April 16, 2017.

46:23.614 --> 46:24.823
YOON SI-HO, BORN ON APRIL 16, 2017

46:27.493 --> 46:29.203
Yoon Si-ho.

46:36.168 --> 46:39.129
-It's a butterfly.
-Look at him smiling.

46:43.550 --> 46:44.551
POLICE

47:09.660 --> 47:11.703
I'm sure it's coming from this side.

47:26.260 --> 47:27.886
What the hell are you exactly?

47:36.228 --> 47:37.479
Hi, kid.

47:40.649 --> 47:41.942
Why aren't you going home?

47:42.442 --> 47:46.196
Mister, watch out for that detective!

47:47.155 --> 47:48.156
Lieutenant Cho?

47:48.240 --> 47:49.658
How did you know this place?

47:50.701 --> 47:52.536
How did you know what happened a year ago?

47:54.621 --> 47:56.456
Help!

47:57.040 --> 47:58.250
See?

47:58.333 --> 48:00.294
My son's scared because of you.

48:01.336 --> 48:02.421
It's you.

48:03.630 --> 48:05.215
You're the culprit.

48:06.425 --> 48:07.801
Help!

48:38.582 --> 48:39.625
Damn it!

48:45.756 --> 48:46.757
Just die.

48:48.550 --> 48:49.551
Hands up!

48:55.849 --> 48:57.601
I'm Lieutenant Cho Chi-yeong.

48:57.684 --> 48:58.894
Show me your ID.

49:04.191 --> 49:05.192
CHO CHI-YEONG

49:06.151 --> 49:07.569
I'm here to find the missing child.

49:14.034 --> 49:16.036
Sir, thank you for your service.

49:19.456 --> 49:20.540
Who is that man?

49:20.624 --> 49:21.917
He's a suspect.

49:22.501 --> 49:23.960
Give me your cuffs. I'll take him in.

49:24.044 --> 49:25.128
Yes, sir.

49:30.550 --> 49:33.637
Mister, wake up.

49:35.597 --> 49:36.765
I'll help you.

49:38.475 --> 49:41.353
We must defeat this evil detective.

49:43.397 --> 49:45.691
Lightning Man, on the move!

49:47.109 --> 49:48.110
No.

49:49.945 --> 49:52.906
You could be put in danger.

49:54.700 --> 49:55.701
Don't do it.

49:57.202 --> 49:58.286
No.

50:09.548 --> 50:13.176
Is the white SUV
parked outside the building

50:13.260 --> 50:14.428
your car, sir?

50:15.053 --> 50:16.763
Yes, why do you ask?

50:19.015 --> 50:20.183
Nothing, sir.

50:45.500 --> 50:47.919
Lightning Man, change of plans.

50:48.503 --> 50:49.671
Hiding.

50:55.969 --> 50:57.596
Damn it.

50:59.473 --> 51:01.266
I wonder where the other punk is hiding.

51:05.979 --> 51:07.397
You're not listening to daddy.

51:08.565 --> 51:10.400
My son needs a scolding.

51:47.437 --> 51:48.939
What did I tell you?

51:50.524 --> 51:52.651
A good boy doesn't make a sound.

51:53.235 --> 51:54.778
Please let me go.

51:56.780 --> 52:00.325
I said you could live with me
if you hang in there just a little.

52:00.992 --> 52:02.702
Must I keep repeating myself?

52:04.246 --> 52:06.498
How many more must die for you to behave?

52:10.544 --> 52:12.254
This won't do. Come here.

52:14.339 --> 52:15.632
Freeze!

52:19.386 --> 52:21.471
-Powering up.
-Powering up.

52:22.138 --> 52:25.350
-Lightning, lightning, lightning…
-Lightning, lightning, lightning…

52:25.433 --> 52:26.977
-…power!
-…power!

52:33.275 --> 52:37.779
Now that I defended justice,
transform back to the mister!

52:50.333 --> 52:53.044
Are you okay?

52:53.128 --> 52:54.546
Mister.

52:54.629 --> 52:57.132
Go to the hospital. Come on.

52:57.215 --> 52:58.216
Okay.

54:00.779 --> 54:02.113
Don't worry.

54:03.531 --> 54:05.367
It's all over now.

54:06.451 --> 54:07.452
Okay.

54:25.804 --> 54:28.848
SHIN I-RANG LAW OFFICE

54:28.932 --> 54:32.102
The phone is turned off. You'll be
directed to voicemail after the tone…

54:33.520 --> 54:34.854
Why is it off?

54:37.065 --> 54:38.775
Could he be in trouble?

54:51.079 --> 54:54.082
LOCAL EMERGENCY MEDICAL CENTER

54:58.545 --> 55:00.046
We have emergency patients. Hurry out!

55:17.272 --> 55:19.941
-Sir, are you okay?
-Sir, wake up!

55:21.192 --> 55:24.029
-Emergency! Please make way!
-Sir, can you hear me?

55:24.112 --> 55:25.864
-Open your eyes.
-Make way.

55:25.947 --> 55:27.657
Wake up, sir. Wake up!

55:31.369 --> 55:32.579
What's going on?

55:32.662 --> 55:34.497
He has a penetrating wound
to the right flank.

55:34.581 --> 55:36.666
Vitals are highly unstable
due to excessive bleeding.

55:36.750 --> 55:37.751
What about his guardian?

55:37.834 --> 55:39.252
We're trying to reach them.

55:44.716 --> 55:45.800
Hello?

55:45.884 --> 55:47.177
This is Seoin Hospital.

55:47.260 --> 55:49.012
Are you Mr. Shin I-rang's guardian?

55:49.804 --> 55:50.805
That's right.

55:51.389 --> 55:54.142
He's been taken to our hospital.
He's in critical condition.

55:54.225 --> 55:56.019
We saw this number on his pendant…

55:57.187 --> 55:58.188
Hello?

55:58.980 --> 55:59.981
Hello?

56:00.648 --> 56:01.649
I'll be there.

56:02.650 --> 56:03.818
I'm on my way right now.

56:07.739 --> 56:10.533
OKCHEON BUILDING

56:11.242 --> 56:12.243
Attorney Han.

56:14.329 --> 56:16.081
Look, I have something to tell…

56:18.333 --> 56:19.334
What's wrong?

56:22.670 --> 56:24.631
What's wrong? Is something going on?

56:25.757 --> 56:27.008
Attorney Shin…

56:27.592 --> 56:28.843
What about Shin I-rang?

56:30.178 --> 56:31.221
The hospital…

56:32.305 --> 56:33.306
I need to go.

56:34.140 --> 56:35.809
You're in no condition to drive.

56:36.392 --> 56:37.727
I need to go to him!

56:57.247 --> 56:58.581
All clean.

56:58.665 --> 57:00.583
-Wipe here, please.
-Sure.

57:01.417 --> 57:02.460
-Bong-su.
-Yes?

57:02.544 --> 57:04.170
Call I-rang and ask him when he's coming.

57:04.254 --> 57:05.338
Okay.

57:13.263 --> 57:14.681
Where's patient Shin I-rang?

57:14.764 --> 57:16.433
Are you Mr. Shin I-rang's guardian?

57:16.516 --> 57:17.517
Yes.

57:17.600 --> 57:18.726
I'm sorry.

57:19.269 --> 57:22.188
He was already unconscious
when he arrived at the hospital.

57:35.326 --> 57:36.536
No.

57:45.962 --> 57:47.422
I should've been there.

57:51.050 --> 57:53.761
I should've been with him.

58:45.188 --> 58:46.189
What…

58:47.398 --> 58:48.399
Am I…

58:49.359 --> 58:50.777
Am I dead?

58:56.282 --> 58:57.283
Am I…

58:59.536 --> 59:01.496
dead for real?

59:29.566 --> 59:31.234
I-rang, Mom is here.

59:31.317 --> 59:32.735
-Doctor.
-Please. I beg you.

59:32.819 --> 59:35.113
We've already tried CPR several times.

59:35.196 --> 59:36.656
Mister, don't go.

59:36.739 --> 59:38.157
Who are you?

59:38.241 --> 59:39.826
-No.
-Who am I?

59:39.909 --> 59:41.202
Our Si-ho will be okay.

59:41.286 --> 59:44.122
Cho Chi-yeong is pleading the Fifth
regarding Si-ho.

59:44.205 --> 59:45.248
I don't know who Si-ho is.

59:45.331 --> 59:46.541
He's a total lunatic.

59:46.624 --> 59:48.293
We still lack evidence.

59:48.376 --> 59:49.502
What do you know?

59:49.586 --> 59:51.546
You said you'd find my mom for me.

59:51.629 --> 59:56.634
Subtitle translation by: Eunjin Erica Kim
